{"id":652332,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/【cdt发布】黎智英及两个儿子、壹传媒高层等7人被/","date":"2020-08-10T01:06:26Z","modified":"2020-08-10T03:16:00Z","title":"【CDT发布】黎智英及两个儿子、壹传媒高层等7人被捕","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652333\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.51.45.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.51.45.png 924w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.51.45-300x123.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.51.45-768x315.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>据明镜、东网以及推特消息，香港壹传媒黎智英于8月10日清晨被警方逮捕，罪名为涉嫌违反国安法第29条中，勾结外国或者境外势力危害国家安全罪，另涉及串谋欺诈及煽动罪。</p>\n<p>另有消息人士透露，警方亦拘捕黎智英的两名儿子黎见恩及黎耀恩，两人涉及勾结外国或者境外势力危害国家安全罪。此外，消息亦指，多名壹传媒高层同时被捕，包括执行董事张剑虹、周达权；而身处海外的黎智英左右手Mark Simon则被警方通缉。<br />\nMark Simon在其社交网站户口贴文，报告黎智英涉嫌勾结外国势力被捕的消息。</p>\n<p>港版国安法实行一个月来，很多人为黎智英担忧，并揣测他或是黄之峰会成为送回大陆的第一人。其被捕消息在社交网络上引起震动与愤怒，并引起人权人士的关注。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_652334\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-652334\" class=\"wp-image-652334\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.57.47.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"406\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.57.47.png 620w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.57.47-300x244.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-652334\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">黎智英的助手Mark Simon在推特上发布黎智英被捕消息</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_652335\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-652335\" class=\"wp-image-652335\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.55.35.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.55.35.png 607w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/屏幕快照-2020-08-09-下午8.55.35-300x250.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-652335\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">黎智英被捕消息立即在社交媒体上引起关注与愤怒</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">💥<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JimmyLaiApple?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@JimmyLaiApple</a>  黎智英 is just arrested for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKong</a> Naional Security Law.</p>\n<p>according to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/initiumnews?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@initiumnews</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/sU2tfGTSvi\">pic.twitter.com/sU2tfGTSvi</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草 Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1292617536018636800?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,38912,38913,38955],"tags":[38683,41441,40679,21970]}